      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん！\n一件目のお仕事終わって、帰ってきました",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おかえり、さくら\nすまないな、今日も同行出来なくて",
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　しょうがないですよ",
      "startTime": 12.2269387245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私達、BIG4入りして以来ずっと忙しいですし\nそれに今や、月ストにリズノワだってBIG4",
      "startTime": 20.1333330154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが忙しくなるのも\n嬉しい悲鳴かもですね！",
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "はは、さくらは相変わらず前向きだな\nでもその通りだ。今が踏ん張りどころの正念場だぞ",
      "startTime": 33.2666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "沢山呼んでもらえるうちに、どれだけ自分達の価値を\n示せるかどうかで、今後の仕事の入り方が変わるからな",
      "startTime": 40.800000445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　大変だなって思う時も少しはありますけど\n月ストやリズノワにも負けてられないですし",
      "startTime": 50.7333337783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "これからも明るく楽しく、出来る仕事をコツコツと\n積み重ねられるよう、頑張ります！",
      "startTime": 58.3666671116,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9200.000063599993,
          "startTime": 67.5666671752
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、体調管理にも気をつけないとな\n意識してオフは差し込むようにしてるけど……ん？",
      "startTime": 65.1666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのスマホ、鳴ってますね\n気にしないで出て下さい",
      "startTime": 72.6486134369,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7118.053738299992,
          "startTime": 79.7666671752
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ありがとう。えっと……橋本さんからだな\nもしもし……えぇっ！？",
      "startTime": 80.500000445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしました？　何か、緊急事態とか……？",
      "startTime": 83.3197513261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "仕事先で、芽衣が体調不良を訴えたらしい\n橋本さんと病院に急行したって……",
      "startTime": 92.7666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！？　芽衣ちゃん、大丈夫なんですか？",
      "startTime": 95.3596812246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分からない、橋本さんも動転してるようだし……\nと、とにかく俺も病院に行ってくるよ",
      "startTime": 103.0666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、次の仕事は私一人で大丈夫です！\nすぐに芽衣ちゃんの所に行ってあげて下さい！",
      "startTime": 110.7666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "私はここで、芽衣ちゃんがなんともありませんように\nって念を送っておきます！　ビビビビビー！",
      "startTime": 117.2333363215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "startTime": 122.6750378925,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1324.9621074999993,
          "startTime": 124
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\n芽衣ちゃんの様子、どうでしたか？",
      "startTime": 126.966672198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今ちょうど部屋まで送ってきたところだ\n食あたりってことだけど、大事には至ってないよ",
      "startTime": 133.4000055313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……良かった\nでも、なんで急に？",
      "startTime": 141.5000055313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "鞄に入れっぱなしのドーナツを食べちゃったらしい\nカビを砂糖のコーティングと勘違いしたそうだ",
      "startTime": 147.8000075658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！？　……そ、そんな勘違いするなんて……",
      "startTime": 151.0706447919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば芽衣ちゃん、今度、アイドル対抗の\nスイーツ大食い大会の番組に出るって言ってましたけど",
      "startTime": 161.8666793187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。でもこの状況だと辞退するしかないだろうな",
      "startTime": 166.5373165448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあお仕事自体もキャンセルするってことですか？",
      "startTime": 171.7636206944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "大会で優勝出来ればCMに出られる～って\n芽衣ちゃんも楽しみにしてたのに",
      "startTime": 180.2333459854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "大会スポンサーでもあるスイーツメーカーのCMだな\nクマのマスコットで有名な",
      "startTime": 186.7925396601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、せっかくなら逃したくない仕事だけど……\n現状、みんな予定が埋まってるから代理もいないし",
      "startTime": 193.3666793187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nそれ、かわりに私が出ます。出たいです！",
      "startTime": 201.8000126521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
